{"word":"Korah","slug":"korah","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Korah</b> <a href=\"#/H7141\">H7141</a> <br/> 1. A son of Esau<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=36&verse=5'>Gen 36:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=36&verse=14'>Gen 36:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=36&verse=18'>Gen 36:18</a><br/> 2. A Korhite Levite:<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=6&verse=18'>Exo 6:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=6&verse=21'>Exo 6:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=6&verse=24'>Exo 6:24</a> <br/> - Jealous of Moses, leads two hundred and fifty princes in an insurrection, and is swallowed up in the earth<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=16'>Num 16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=26&verse=10'>Num 26:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=11&verse=6'>Deu 11:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=106&verse=17'>Psa 106:17</a>; <a href='B:'></a> <br/> 3. Son of Hebron<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=2&verse=43'>1Ch 2:43</a><br/> 4. Son of Kohath:<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=6&verse=22'>1Ch 6:22</a><br/> Reference titles to selected Psalms<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=42&verse=11'>Psa 42:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=45'>Psa 45</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=87'>Psa 87</a>"}]}